Description: The TADA Community Hub offers a collaborative platform for users 
    to share templates that support reproducible TADA workflows. This R package and 
    GitHub repository includes criteria and methods files authored, reviewed, and
    contributed by TADA community members such as EPA, states, tribes, and territories.
